<section id="about">
  <h3>About the Project</h3>
  <p>The DAKODA project focuses on building and exploring a learner corpus infrastructure with standardized formats (CAS) and annotated datasets across multiple corpora. This infrastructure supports advanced linguistic research and tool development.</p>
</section>

<section id="corpora">
  <h3>Corpora Overview</h3>
  <p>A variety of corpora are integrated into the DAKODA infrastructure, representing different modalities, tasks, and learner types. For corpus-specific metadata and download options, visit the <a href="/repository/">Repository</a>.</p>
</section>

